cross: Cymbidium Phar Lap x Cymbidium Miss Muffet

measurements.description:
Four hundred ninety-three flowers and one hundred ninety-three buds on twenty-three pendant inflorescences
    on a vigorous plant, 116 cm wide, grown in a 25 cm pot; plant in excellent condition, with inflorescences
    spread evenly around the plant; sepals and petals mahogany; lip saturated burgundy;	pollen cap white;
    substance firm; texture matte.
